Job Description
Share
We are currently looking to recruit a Senior Chef De Partie to join our Kitchen team.
You will supervise and control the subordinates assigned to your shift under the direct guidance and instructions of the Executive Chef /Outlet Chef. You will also be responsible for the proper efficiency and profitable functioning of the assigned Kitchen.
You will need to be flexible with working hours and be a team player. Fluency in English is required and previous kitchen experience in a similar position is preferred.
